 int value) {\n            return \"int:\" + value;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 781, "output": 858, "cacheRead": 32256, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 33895, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778596688084, "responseId": "resp_0c1604060f52859f016a033b50fadc8194964c6550c482653e"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_yyqgqmnxiHAk04jlMLWidNjC|fc_0c1604060f52859f016a033b59f9808194b41057a87055917b", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1211 bytes to tests/src/org.apache.velocity/velocity/1.5/src/test/java/org_apache_velocity/velocity/MethodMapTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778596701204}]}
